{"tid":948362,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿Sa：「結婚4年了，依然是處女。」","createTime":"2018-12-20T04:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T06:15:53.000Z","uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c6b0db460408de5571c994db40b87f11fe9f26","tid":948362,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"影》畫面震撼！阿Sa全裸出浴自爆是「處女」<br />\n2018年12月19日 10:06 中時電子報 黃詩淳／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-12-19/590/20181219001563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-12-19%2F590%2F20181219001563.jpg&h=98d17f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿Sa全裸濕身露美背。(圖／翻攝自youtube)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-12-19/590/20181219001566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-12-19%2F590%2F20181219001566.jpg&h=d031712d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿Sa背全裸，堪稱是她從影以來最性感的演出。(圖／翻攝自youtube)<br />\n<br />\n香港女團TWINS成員蔡卓妍(阿Sa)過去多以清純玉女形象示人，近年來不斷挑戰自我，繼在電影《雛妓》的大膽演出後，現新片又有大突破，不僅全裸濕身坐在浴缸內，更配上「結婚4年了，依然是處女！」獨白，預告片曝光後，震撼外界。<br />\n<br />\n阿Sa在電影《雛妓》中，不僅有被摸乳激情性愛畫面，還說出「我有讓你上過！」大尺度對話，形象180度轉變，令人印象深刻，而現她又有一突破之作，就是在新片《非分熟女》中有大膽出浴戲，全裸濕身的她坐在浴缸中，雖然僅露出性感美背，但搭配「結婚4年了，依然是處女！」獨白，短短1分鐘預告，就震撼不少人。<br />\n<br />\n而阿Sa坦言，在接下角色後，就清楚了解角色和整個故事內容，所以只要符合劇情需要，又拿表達劇中女主的內心掙扎，她欣然接受，而這次背部全裸，堪稱是她從影以來最性感的演出，她笑說：「前面有做了保護措施，別緊張，好安全的！不過，畫面有幾個角度很震撼，大家拭目以待。」<br />\n<br />\n《非分熟女》由阿Sa和吳慷仁主演，她在電影中，飾演獨生女小敏，和丈夫結婚4年沒有過性生活，在遇到吳慷仁飾演的型男廚師後，決定跳出框架，是部探討女性身體自主的愛情電影。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181219001552-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181219001552-260404&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=8fdc2e16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181219001552-260404</a>"},{"pid":"e6bf931018d155d8c53141bf5d383d8257d3e507","tid":948362,"uid":107364,"like":9,"dislike":14,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4af7fb398da3af0003e866e43fa949bb51b08b5f","tid":948362,"uid":109462,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"&rarr; kent: 還好不是阿嬌說的<br />\n&rarr; VVizZ: 鄭中基表示:早就Ｏ膩<br />\n&rarr; occboy: 我以為是另一位&hellip;那還可以<br />\n推 yesgogo: 難道鄭中基？？<br />\n&rarr; Krishna: 嚇死我，還以為冠C被認證不舉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1545276638.A.F09.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1545276638.A.F09.html&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=326220d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1545276638.A.F09.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b24266fbe086313a23a3eb6de43b63c2b506a53","tid":948362,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"今日是處女"},{"pid":"fbf29ae35ab7a64d5686ca986b5a31c8ee26f4a8","tid":948362,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"我有讓你上過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1394f145698dd97ce208ece81d72c15ad2202db","tid":948362,"uid":78470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/141856_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F141856_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=42a2114d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"761802252df449a8df29fbbf3ecadf7a40a0a1f0","tid":948362,"uid":3893,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:16:32.